42int
43kex_dh_keygen(struct kex *kex)
44{
45 switch (kex->kex_type) {
46 case KEX_DH_GRP1_SHA1:
47 kex->dh = dh_new_group1();
48 break;
49 case KEX_DH_GRP14_SHA1:
50 case KEX_DH_GRP14_SHA256:
51 kex->dh = dh_new_group14();
52 break;
53 case KEX_DH_GRP16_SHA512:
54 kex->dh = dh_new_group16();
55 break;
56 case KEX_DH_GRP18_SHA512:
57 kex->dh = dh_new_group18();
58 break;
59 default:
60 return SSH_ERR_INVALID_ARGUMENT;
61 }
62 if (kex->dh == NULL)
63 return SSH_ERR_ALLOC_FAIL;
64 return (dh_gen_key(kex->dh, kex->we_need * 8));
65}
66
67int
68kex_dh_compute_key(struct kex *kex, BIGNUM *dh_pub, struct sshbuf *out)
69{
70 BIGNUM *shared_secret = NULL;
71 u_char *kbuf = NULL;
72 size_t klen = 0;
73 int kout, r;
74
75#ifdef DEBUG_KEXDH
76 fprintf(stderr, "dh_pub= ");
77 BN_print_fp(stderr, dh_pub);
78 fprintf(stderr, "\n");
79 debug("bits %d", BN_num_bits(dh_pub));
80 DHparams_print_fp(stderr, kex->dh);
81 fprintf(stderr, "\n");
82#endif
83
84 if (!dh_pub_is_valid(kex->dh, dh_pub)) {
85 r = SSH_ERR_MESSAGE_INCOMPLETE;
86 goto out;
87 }
88 klen = DH_size(kex->dh);
89 if ((kbuf = malloc(klen)) == NULL ||
90 (shared_secret = BN_new()) == NULL) {
91 r = SSH_ERR_ALLOC_FAIL;
92 goto out;
93 }
94 if ((kout = DH_compute_key(kbuf, dh_pub, kex->dh)) < 0 ||
95 BN_bin2bn(kbuf, kout, shared_secret) == NULL) {
96 r = SSH_ERR_LIBCRYPTO_ERROR;
97 goto out;
98 }
99#ifdef DEBUG_KEXDH
100 dump_digest("shared secret", kbuf, kout);
101#endif
102 r = sshbuf_put_bignum2(out, shared_secret);
103 out:
104 freezero(kbuf, klen);
105 BN_clear_free(shared_secret);
106 return r;
107}
108
109int
110kex_dh_keypair(struct kex *kex)
111{
112 const BIGNUM *pub_key;
113 struct sshbuf *buf = NULL;
114 int r;
115
116 if ((r = kex_dh_keygen(kex)) != 0)
117 return r;
118 DH_get0_key(kex->dh, &pub_key, NULL);
119 if ((buf = sshbuf_new()) == NULL)
120 return SSH_ERR_ALLOC_FAIL;
121 if ((r = sshbuf_put_bignum2(buf, pub_key)) != 0 ||
122 (r = sshbuf_get_u32(buf, NULL)) != 0)
123 goto out;
124#ifdef DEBUG_KEXDH
125 DHparams_print_fp(stderr, kex->dh);
126 fprintf(stderr, "pub= ");
127 BN_print_fp(stderr, pub_key);
128 fprintf(stderr, "\n");
129#endif
130 kex->client_pub = buf;
131 buf = NULL;
132 out:
133 sshbuf_free(buf);
134 return r;
135}
136
137int
138kex_dh_enc(struct kex *kex, const struct sshbuf *client_blob,
139 struct sshbuf **server_blobp, struct sshbuf **shared_secretp)
140{
141 const BIGNUM *pub_key;
142 struct sshbuf *server_blob = NULL;
143 int r;
144
145 *server_blobp = NULL;
146 *shared_secretp = NULL;
147
148 if ((r = kex_dh_keygen(kex)) != 0)
149 goto out;
150 DH_get0_key(kex->dh, &pub_key, NULL);
151 if ((server_blob = sshbuf_new()) == NULL) {
152 r = SSH_ERR_ALLOC_FAIL;
153 goto out;
154 }
155 if ((r = sshbuf_put_bignum2(server_blob, pub_key)) != 0 ||
156 (r = sshbuf_get_u32(server_blob, NULL)) != 0)
157 goto out;
158 if ((r = kex_dh_dec(kex, client_blob, shared_secretp)) != 0)
159 goto out;
160 *server_blobp = server_blob;
161 server_blob = NULL;
162 out:
163 DH_free(kex->dh);
164 kex->dh = NULL;
165 sshbuf_free(server_blob);
166 return r;
167}
168
169int
170kex_dh_dec(struct kex *kex, const struct sshbuf *dh_blob,
171 struct sshbuf **shared_secretp)
172{
173 struct sshbuf *buf = NULL;
174 BIGNUM *dh_pub = NULL;
175 int r;
176
177 *shared_secretp = NULL;
178
179 if ((buf = sshbuf_new()) == NULL) {
180 r = SSH_ERR_ALLOC_FAIL;
181 goto out;
182 }
183 if ((r = sshbuf_put_stringb(buf, dh_blob)) != 0 ||
184 (r = sshbuf_get_bignum2(buf, &dh_pub)) != 0)
185 goto out;
186 sshbuf_reset(buf);
187 if ((r = kex_dh_compute_key(kex, dh_pub, buf)) != 0)
188 goto out;
189 *shared_secretp = buf;
190 buf = NULL;
191 out:
192 DH_free(kex->dh);
193 kex->dh = NULL;
194 sshbuf_free(buf);
195 return r;
196}
